SOFTWARE PACKAGE FOR SCRAPING DYNAMIC WEBSITES




Author: Andreu Jov√©




INSTALLATION OF THIS PACKAGE:

========================================================================

1) Open terminal.

2) Go to the current directory where you want the cloned directory to be added using 'cd'.

3) Run the command: $git clone https://github.com/AndreuJove/seleniumCrawler

4) Install requirements.txt if it's possible in a virtual environment. 

5) Change path of the dataset of websites URLs if it's required.

5) Run the following command:
    $ python3 crawler_selenium.py
    
========================================================================